WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:11.067 --> 00:00:21.501
MITSUBISHI 
Pajero Sport 3.0 V6

00:00:23.834 --> 00:00:27.734
While Chevrolet takes "public debut" the all-new TrailBlazer

00:00:30.801 --> 00:00:35.267
Mitsubishi quietly introduces 
"Pajero Sport V6 3.0 MIVEC" at its pavillion of 33RDBiMS

00:00:38.801 --> 00:00:43.967
It definitely comes with V6 3.0 MIVEC engine 
which Mitsubishi Motors Thailand exported to overseas

00:00:44.067 --> 00:00:49.167
Maximum Power: 162kw @ 6,250rpm
Maximum Torque: 281nm @ 4,000rpm

00:00:49.201 --> 00:00:52.234
219 HP

00:00:52.301 --> 00:00:55.234
5-Speed Automatic with Sportronic and Manual mode

00:00:55.267 --> 00:00:57.467
With shift paddles (GT only)

00:00:59.267 --> 00:01:02.534
Available as 4x4 or 4x2, GLS &amp; GT

00:01:05.834 --> 00:01:08.467
LED lamps by rear view mirrors

00:01:08.767 --> 00:01:10.934
Mitsubishi's "RISE" body structure 
(Reinforced Impact Safety Evolution)

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.267
Anti-Theft

00:01:16.301 --> 00:01:20.000
Front: Double Wishbone, Coil Springs, Stabilizer bar
Rear: 3-link Torque Arm, Coil Springs, Stabilizer bar

00:01:22.167 --> 00:01:27.734
Not only beared unusual power (to Thai market), 
interior is also unusual "Black Interior"

00:01:27.734 --> 00:01:31.901
"Absolute equipped" like never before

00:01:32.334 --> 00:01:34.767
Auto Cruise Control on steering wheel

00:01:34.834 --> 00:01:37.634
Tri-circle fluorescent gauge

00:01:39.634 --> 00:01:42.701
7-inch screen for entertainment and navigation system, 
with Bluetooth and hub for AUX/USB

00:01:42.734 --> 00:01:45.201
As well as display for back camera

00:01:45.267 --> 00:01:48.101
Tri-zone Climate Control

00:01:48.134 --> 00:01:50.434
Tweeter speakers

00:01:50.467 --> 00:01:53.101
Electric rear view mirrors

00:01:56.234 --> 00:02:00.867
For the first time ever: 10.2-inch LCD screen

00:02:02.201 --> 00:02:06.767
New dark tone leather upholstery

00:02:19.434 --> 00:02:22.401
But still gave only dual airbags

00:02:23.601 --> 00:02:26.601
This dark blue paintjob comes exclusively with this version

00:02:29.701 --> 00:02:34.334
So this is Thailand's first ever V6 powered PPV

00:02:34.434 --> 00:02:39.667
And that has become automatically "flagship model", 
no need to be curious

00:02:41.734 --> 00:02:47.167
If you don't fear of "V6 consumption"

